article.description: — Radshad Davis had 15 points as Florida International topped Middle Tennessee 68-55 on Friday night.
article.headline: Davis scores 15 to carry FIU past Middle Tennessee 68-55
article.linkText: Davis scores 15 to carry FIU past Middle Tennessee 68-55
article.story: MURFREESBORO, Tenn. -- — Radshad Davis had 15 points as Florida International topped Middle Tennessee 68-55 on Friday night. Tevin Brewer had 13 points for FIU (8-3, 2-1 Conference USA). Antonio Daye Jr. added 13 points and seven rebounds. Dimon Carrigan had three blocks. Jalen Jordan had 17 points for the Blue Raiders (2-5, 0-1). ------ For more AP college basketball coverage: https://apnews.com/Collegebasketball and http://twitter.com/AP--Top25 ------ This was generated by Automated Insights, http://www.automatedinsights.com/ap, using data from STATS LLC, https://www.stats.com
